## Technical Notes

### Hydration Warning Fix
Added `suppressHydrationWarning` to `<html>` and `<body>` elements in `layout.tsx` to prevent React errors from browser extensions modifying HTML attributes.

### RTL Support
- All components support RTL for Arabic locale
- Using logical properties (`ms-`, `me-`, `ps-`, `pe-`, `border-s-`, etc.)
- RTL rotation for directional icons

### Responsive Design
- Mobile-first approach
- Breakpoints: `sm`, `md`, `lg`, `xl`
- Collapsible mobile menu
- Responsive grids

### i18n
- Using `useI18n()` hook from `@/lib/i18n-context`
- Inline locale checks: `locale === 'ar' ? arabicText : englishText`
- Translations stored in `lib/i18n-context.tsx`

